      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned dual-VANOS system. This example has been meticulously curated, with documented subframe reinforcement, rod bearing replacement, and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure mechanical longevity. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing unparalleled driver engagement. The chassis is sharpened by Bilstein PSS10 adjustable dampers, while the exterior retains its factory-original finish with uniform paint thickness. The cabin is equally impeccable, featuring supple Nappa leather with no evidence of bolster compression or UV damage. A technically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
